{"id":15113,"title":"Navigating through 'a labyrinth' of guidance.","abstract":"Devising a strategy to deliver safe water to thousands of outlets spread across numerous buildings is always going to be a challenge, so how do you navigate your way through a bewildering labyrinth of sometimes contradictory guidance documents? Is there, in fact, simply too much guidance? Posing this question at a recent one-day conference on waterborne infections in healthcare facilities, Paul Nolan, authorised water engineer (AE), and operations manager for PFI provider, Lend Lease, took delegates through a review of the latest guidance and regulations, as Susan Pearson reports.","date":"2014-10-06","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25282983","annotations":[{"name":"Health care","weight":0.494809,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Water","weight":0.287046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Water"},{"name":"Navigation","weight":0.210873,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Navigation"},{"name":"Engineer","weight":0.186224,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engineer"},{"name":"Strategy","weight":0.151404,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy"},{"name":"Drinking water","weight":0.131186,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drinking_water"},{"name":"Regulation","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regulation"},{"name":"Lease","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lease"},{"name":"American English","weight":0.0332387,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_English"},{"name":"Labyrinth","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Labyrinth"},{"name":"Lend-Lease","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lend-Lease"},{"name":"Private finance initiative","weight":0.0297972,"wiki